## Get the product descriptions

### v1

By default, with “Accept-version” v1

item.description:
The purpose of the Product API is to declare in ytem all the GTINs & SKUs to be used and also the product attached description such as label, model, color size, category.

## 1.1 Characteristics

*   The product API endpoints include new fields to be compatible with the new EPCIS event structure and ILMDs.
*   Company prefix is automatically decoded from GTIN-14 when it is not provided during product creation
*   The Automatic Company Prefix decoding from a GTIN is automated based on the GS1 Company Prefix Length Table.
